  <Section Title="Declaration">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[struct WindowInfoAppKit : public IFrameBuffer::WindowInfoBase;]]></Code>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>WindowInfoAppKit</TypeRef> structure describes an AppKit view for framebuffer presentation on macOS.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      Availability: macOS when <TypeRef>COBALT_RENDERER_APPKIT_SUPPORT</TypeRef> is enabled. This is automatically enabled on macOS unless platform binding selection is manual.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
